Turns out [Anandtech](http://www.anandtech.com/) has started providing some [Mac](http://www.anandtech.com/mac/) coverage.  Anand starts off with [A Month with a Mac: A Die-Hard PC User's Perspective](http://www.anandtech.com/mac/showdoc.aspx?i=2232) providing his take on the Mac experience to the "uninitiated" with a hefty Dual-G5 desktop.  This led to the [mobile experience](http://www.anandtech.com/mac/showdoc.aspx?i=2326) with a Powerbook.  Most recently, he's taken a look at the [Mac mini](http://www.anandtech.com/mac/showdoc.aspx?i=2328).